# Schema Documentation

Welcome to the Schemas documentation.

This site contains human-readable explanations of all schemas in this repository, including:

- Field descriptions
- Validation rules
- Known limitations
- Runtime compatibility notes

## Available Schemas

### Roblox
- **Fast Flags**  
  Configuration validation for Roblox `ClientAppSettings.json`, including allow-listed and community-discovered flags.

More schemas will be added over time.
